Response:  The first part of the question is "ལས་འཛིན་ཅིག་གིས་ལས་བྱེད་རེ་རེ་ལ་ཟླ་རེར་ཨ་སྒོრ་". This can be translated to "What are the causes and conditions that lead to the emergence of phenomena?" Now let's break it down further. "ལས" means "causes", "འཛིན" means "conditions", "ཅིག" means "emerge", "གིས" means "and", "ལས" means "phenomena", "བྱེད" means "to arise", "རེ" means "from", "རེ་རེ" means "what", "ལ་" means "and", "ཟླ" means "the world", "རེར" means "emerges", "ཨ" means "and", "སྒོր" means "in what way". So the question is asking about the causes and conditions that lead to the emergence of phenomena in the world.
